overview.en: iEOS is an inverse synthetic EOS token enabled by the [Synthetix protocol](https://synthetix.io). It inversely tracks the price of EOS through price feeds supplied by [Chainlinkâ€™s](https://chain.link) decentralized network of oracles. It can be traded without slippage for other assets native to the Synthetix protocol at [Kwenta](https://kwenta.io) or [Synthetix.Exchange](https://synthetix.exchange). More information about Inverse Synths can be found in the [Synthetix Docs](https://docs.synthetix.io/tokens/#inverse-isynths).
